videos.description: Saivion Smith intercepts Drew Lock on his first pass of the game and takes it inside the 10-yard line.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Alabama picks off Lock’s 1st pass) 2018/10/13 ESHEET

videos.headline: Alabama picks off Lock's 1st pass

videos.description: Drew Lock fires a 20-yard touchdown after having an eternity in the pocket.
videos.headline: Lock directs traffic then throws 20-yard dart for TD

videos.description: Tua Tagovailoa throws a touchdown to Irv Smith Jr. and Alabama goes up 20-10.
videos.headline: Tua finds back of end zone for score

videos.description: Alabama forces Drew Lock to fumble, then score on a 13-yard pass on the next play.
videos.headline: Alabama recovers fumble, scores on next play

videos.description: Tua Tagovailoa reinjures his right knee while sliding for a first down and is taken out of the game.
videos.headline: Tua exits game after reinjuring right leg

videos.description: Jalen Hurts throws a perfect pass for Alabama to score two plays later.
videos.headline: Hurts throws dime to set Alabama up for TD

videos.description: Tua Tagovailoa throws for 265 yards and three scores before leaving the game with a right leg injury as Alabama cruises past Missouri 39-10.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Highlight (Tua injury doesn’t stop Alabama from another win) 2018/10/13 ESHEET SOTFULL

videos.headline: Tua injury doesn't stop Alabama from another win

videos.description: Nick Saban is impressed with the defensive outcome and adds that Tua Tagovailoa is "OK" despite not returning to the game.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Interview (Saban happy with team’s performance, says Tua is ‘OK’) 2018/10/13

videos.headline: Saban happy with team's performance, says Tua is 'OK'
